text: A pair of hairstylists who tested positive for the coronavirus have potentially exposed at least 140 clients at a Great Clips in Springfield, MO. Springfield is in the Ozarks where many people are partying without precautions. It's a ticking time bomb. https://t.co/GfD3Phm1VH
